HEADWORD: Sonification
<hw>Son`i*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sonus</ets> sound + <ets>-ficare</ets> (in comp.) to make. See
<er>-fy</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of producing sound, as the
stridulation of insects.</def>⟦br⟧
